fix: allow /img paths in maintenance mode (#40701)

fix: allow /img paths on maintenance mode
commits.diff:
diff --git a/apps/studio/next.config.js b/apps/studio/next.config.js
index 2177d91b3a9f0..8fd06b57628d8 100644
--- a/apps/studio/next.config.js
+++ b/apps/studio/next.config.js
@@ -442,7 +442,7 @@ const nextConfig = {
       ...(process.env.MAINTENANCE_MODE === 'true'
         ? [
             {
-              source: '/((?!maintenance).*)', // Redirect all paths except /maintenance
+              source: '/((?!maintenance|img).*)', // Redirect all paths except /maintenance and /img
               destination: '/maintenance',
               permanent: false,
             },
